videos.description: Luke Maye is wide open for the 3-pointer as the Tar Heels keep it close with Notre Dame early.
videos.headline: Maye drains early 3 for UNC

videos.description: Nate Laszewski drains a 3-pointer at the end of the first half to give the Fighting Irish the lead at halftime over North Carolina.
videos.headline: Laszewski drains 3 at end of half

videos.description: Nassir Little breaks free for a monster two-handed slam that gets the UNC crowd hyped.
videos.headline: Little throws down huge dunk
